    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a reliable daily driver for several years. The engine is functional and the transmission shifts through all gears, though you may notice some minor lag during acceleration. Cosmetically, there are visible scratches on the exterior paint and some staining on the interior upholstery consistent with its age. While it remains roadworthy and passed its last inspection, a buyer should expect to address some minor maintenance items in the near future to keep it running optimally.",
