    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. It currently requires significant mechanical attention to be safely roadworthy, including engine diagnostics and suspension work. The exterior has multiple deep scratches, significant paint oxidation, and several large dents on the passenger side panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing, and the electronics are intermittent. This is an honest assessment for a buyer prepared to invest time and resources into a full restoration.",
